        {
            "_id": "jERkiSsIUnQegewH",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Edge Skate",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The facet guardian dashes forward quickly, sliding on the knife-edge of one of its facets. It moves up to its Speed and makes one mirror's edge Strike against any number of creatures it passes adjacent to during its movement. These attacks contribute to the facet guardian's multiple attack penalty, but the penalty does not increase until all attacks are complete.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "move"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "sptNG7yVCKDcGuCA",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Flat-Pack",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The facet guardian quickly unfolds for storage against a flat surface or refolds itself into humanoid shape. The surface must be flat and large enough to contain the guardian in its unfolded state, at least 5 feet by 10 feet, though it can be oriented in any direction. When in unfolded form, the facet guardian cannot take any action except Flat-Pack to refold, and its Deception DC to Impersonate an inanimate mural increase to DC 22.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "manipulate"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        }
